boxes.header_text:
IF ANY SCREW-TYPE ANCHORAGE PENETRATES THE EXTERIOR METAL WALL OR
ROOF PANELS AND MISSES THE INTENDED METAL FRAMING, THE SCREW SHOULD
BE LEFT IN PLACE OR PATCHED TO AVOID LEAVING A HOLE IN THE EXTERIOR
SHEATHING. IF ANY HOLE CANNOT BE SUFFICIENTLY PATCHED TO ENSURE
PERMANENT WEATHERTIGHTNESS, THE METAL PANEL SHALL BE REPLACED.
